      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a great start, thanks. I think it's a bit too \"standard\" though. Can you add a little more punch to it? Maybe lean into the idea of \"escaping the daily grind\" or \"fighting off the exhaustion\" that comes with a long workday? I want it to feel like a relief for people who are really struggling with their current setup.",
